<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f2f2f2; border-color: #004875; border-width: 10px; padding: 30px; border-style: solid; border-radius: 20px; max-width:600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    <div>
        <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
        <p>Thanks for booking your ride with Devitex!</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Pickup: {{pickup}}</li>
            <li>Destination: {{destination}}</li>
            <li>Date: {{date}}</li>
            <li>Time: {{time}}</li>
            <li>Passengers: {{passengers}}</li>
            <li>Vehicle: {{vehicle}}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We'll contact you shortly to confirm the booking.</p>
        <p><em>Submitted on {{submitted_at}}</em></p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>